3. 養聲
廣東話：佢最近喺唱歌，所以好注意養聲，唔好過份用力。
English: He is singing recently, so he pays attention to taking care of his voice and doesn't use too much force.

4. 票尾
廣東話：你睇下張票尾，上面寫咗你嘅簽名。
English: Look at the stub of the ticket, it has your signature written on it.

5. hacker
廣東話：佢係個黑客，最近好活躍喺網上搵漏洞。
English: He is a hacker, he is quite active in finding vulnerabilities on the internet recently.

6. 石斛蘭
廣東話：呢盆石斛蘭長得好，真係好靚。
English: This石斛蘭 is growing well, it is really beautiful.

7. 吊詭
廣東話：呢個情況好吊詭，佢話唔會做，結果又做咗。
English: This situation is very paradoxical, he said he wouldn't do it, but in the end he did.

8. 吊詭
廣東話：佢嘅話好吊詭，似非而是，令人好困惑。
English: His words are very paradoxical, seeming not to be but actually being, confusing people.

9. 各為其主
廣東話：兩家公司各為其主，最後竟然打咗架。
English: The two companies acted for their own masters, and in the end they even fought.

10. 軨蓋
廣東話：佢一開口就係軨蓋，真係好粗魯。
English: As soon as he opened his mouth, it was a 呔軨，he is really rude.

11. 打哥夫
廣東話：佢週末喜歡打哥夫，好享受。
English: He likes to play golf on weekends, he enjoys it very much.

12. 免揀
廣東話：呢度係免揀嘅，你直接拎走就好。
English: This is a no-choice item, you can just take it directly.

13. 擺闊佬
廣東話：佢好愛擺闊佬，每次食飯都叫最貴嘅菜。
English: He loves to show off his wealth, every time he eats he orders the most expensive dishes.

14. 廣播劇
廣東話：我哋以前好鍾意聽廣播劇，好有畫面感。
English: We used to love listening to radio dramas, they are very vivid.

15. 錄影機
廣東話：佢買咗部新錄影機，好方便。
English: He bought a new video recorder, it is very convenient.

16. 吟詩吟唔甩
廣東話：佢嘅證據好充分，真係吟詩吟唔甩。
English: His evidence is very sufficient, he really cannot deny it.

17. 佈道大會
廣東話：佢哋下個月會舉行佈道大會，好多人會去。
English: They will hold a missionary meeting next month, many people will go.

18. 寫手
廣東話：佢係個專業寫手，寫文章好快。
English: He is a professional writer, he writes articles very quickly.

19. 寫手
廣東話：佢係個代寫手，幫人寫論文。
English: He is a ghostwriter, he helps people write papers.

20. 代打
廣東話：佢係個好代打，好多人請佢打機。
English: He is a good substitute player, many people ask him to play games.

21. 茶碗
廣東話：佢用個日本茶碗飲茶，好有味道。
English: He drinks tea with a Japanese tea bowl, it is very flavorful.

22. 茶隔
廣東話：飲茶嘅時候，記得用茶隔將茶葉同茶湯分開。
English: When drinking tea, remember to use a tea strainer to separate the tea leaves from the tea soup.

23. 只許州官放火，不准百姓點燈
廣東話：佢好自私，只許州官放火，不准百姓點燈。
English: He is very selfish, he allows himself to do whatever he wants, but restricts the common people.

24. 獨唱
廣東話：佢今日係獨唱，唔係同人一齊唱。
English: He is singing solo today, not singing with others.

25. 快人快事
廣東話：佢係個快人快事，做嘢好爽快。
English: He is a straightforward person, he does things very quickly and straightforwardly.

26. 四腳獸
廣東話：佢哋喺廁所入面做四腳獸，真係好羞恥。
English: They are doing something in the toilet, it is really shameful.

27. 無米粥
廣東話：呢個項目目前係煲無米粥，好多細節都未著落。
English: This project is currently in the preliminary stage, many details are not yet settled.

28. 義會
廣東話：佢哋以前會開義會，幫人借錢。
English: They used to hold fundraising meetings, helping people borrow money.

29. 榜文
廣東話：佢貼咗張榜文喺牆上面，好多人睇。
English: He posted a notice on the wall, many people saw it.

30. MK 名
廣東話：佢個 MK 名好特別，好多人唔識。
English: His MK name is very special, many people don't know it. [end of text]


